        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_quote",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " In the editor I’ve added a feature so that I can move through a flow automatically while recording a video. "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\nSo cool! Love seeing this after discovering the Code Tours Extension in VS Code last week. Really digging this!\n\nI also like the spatial organisation and color coding of your environment. Together with the tour, you’re starting to build a map of a program with different islands but instead of just dropping someone into this new world, you offer a map/tour guide with it. This is fantastic."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
